        "body" : "can you comment why vs justing using `Nil`? I guess you are using `null` to signal that you are not in a localRunLoop. Is that right? Can you comment?\r\n\r\nCould it be `NonEmptyList[Runnable]` I wonder, and then use the `null` trick on that?",
